---
title: American Beef Rissoles with Sweetcorn Slaw & Potato Fries
description: Roll up a taste of America into these bite-sized morsels of flavour! Studded with corn kernels and served with a creamy slaw, potato fries and smokey BBQ sauce for dipping, this is a moreish meal that will have you hooked!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bd9333bae08b513645e2f72-ce282774.jpg
